{"tid":2270650,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［鬼滅］Feel The RAGE","createTime":"2020-11-04T06:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T11:53:31.000Z","uid":260866,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b285aba1b92dc76e555b3c97d4320c5ea5a58ec","tid":2270650,"uid":260866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T06:43:12.000Z","msg":"我都覺得鬼滅其實主旋律就係講憤怒同埋仇恨，血海深仇點樣令人冷靜、有動力，最終一步步慢慢成功斬殺鬼王。<br />\n<br />\n雖然王道，但故事簡單直接，香港人，NEVER FORGET, NEVER FORGIVE, NEVER SURRENDER. <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3x4nmOT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3x4nmOT.png&h=feb07c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">劍術像浪客壯麗 或你怕死像我妻 <br />\n要是同路去 未怕亂世</span></span></span></strong></span><br />\n#鬼滅之日<br />\n<span class=\"large\"><span class=\"red\">如果 要把鬼滅<br />\n要惡人粉碎<br />\n唯獨你前來<br />\n盡處跨過去<br />\n你我他 能互相組隊<br />\n路遙沒顧慮</span></span>"},{"pid":"d60ba16789d65be9a92435333e90aa5b8b95bec5","tid":2270650,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:23:04.000Z","msg":"鬼滅之日都有負皮<br />\n連登係咪真係已經反鬼滅反到盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02790933539b180fa7fb1ab41f64ba7f234ad2ba","tid":2270650,"uid":260866,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d60ba16789d65be9a92435333e90aa5b8b95bec5","tid":2270650,"uid":370062,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T11:23:04.000Z","msg":"鬼滅之日都有負皮<br />\n連登係咪真係已經反鬼滅反到盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T11:53:31.000Z","msg":"可能係藍絲港豬比負皮呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}